这会很艰难。

175
00:10:12.500 --> 00:10:17.796
But you've got to communicate your vision so passionately, so strongly,
但你必须充满激情地把你的想法 与他人交流，

176
00:10:17.820 --> 00:10:21.196
that everybody knows what the goal is
让每个人都知道目标是什么,

177
00:10:21.220 --> 00:10:23.996
