我们败得更好，我们再次尝试， 我们再次败得更好。

214
00:12:19.460 --> 00:12:23.796
Maybe after we've tried 15 times, we've mastered some specific subject,
也许在我们尝试了15次后， 我们掌握到了特定技能，

215
00:12:23.820 --> 00:12:27.460
so you want to minimize the time it takes to try those 15 times.
所以你需要缩短这15次尝试的时间。

216
00:12:27.876 --> 00:12:31.090
We optimize on trust. We encourage diversity.
我们优化信任， 我们鼓励多样性。

217
00:12:31.260 --> 00:12:33.516
You need to communicate your vision so strongly
你需要强烈传达你的愿景，

218
00:12:33.540 --> 00:12:38.436
so that everybody can translate it into their own context
这样每个人都可以把 它转变为自己的理解，

219
00:12:38.460 --> 00:12:42.356
because language is an incredibly strong
因为语言是一种非常强大的

220
00:12:42.380 --> 00:12:46.180
inclusionary and exclusionary social marker.
兼具包含性和排他性的社会标志。

221
00:12:48.620 --> 00:12:51.876
This one-brand-fits-all message --
那些所谓的适用于任何企业的讯息，

222
00:12:51.900 --> 00:12:53.116
forget it!
忘掉它！

223
00:12:52.586 --> 00:12:55.396
That's what they teach you at business school -- it doesn't work.
那是商业院教你的东西——它行不通。

224
00:12:55.396 --> 00:13:00.296
Or at least, it doesn't give you the cost-efficiency advantage
或者至少，它不会给你 带来集群工作的

