我贡献我知道的东西。

238
00:13:41.540 --> 00:13:43.276
Make people aware of this diversity.
让人们意识到多样性，

239
00:13:43.300 --> 00:13:45.980
Finally, scalability. Get feet on the ground.
最后，规模化的，脚踏实地。

240
00:13:46.700 --> 00:13:50.156
Again, in business school, they teach you to use a lean organization.
再一次，在商学院，他们教授你 使用精简的组织结构。

